room_title: Escape room "Dead Line" by Locked & Coded in Charleston (WV)
room_description: An increase in missing people has lead to your team's investigation. A 9-1-1 operator has received a lead that the coroner is behind all of this. It is your job to search for the missing people without getting caught in danger. If we do not hear back from you in one hour, we will send back up.
